Market Segmentation
By Technology
1.	AI-Based Driving Assessment – Uses AI algorithms for automated scoring and analysis.
2.	IoT-Enabled Smart Sensors – Monitors driver behavior and test conditions in real time.
3.	Cloud-Based Driving Test Solutions – Stores and processes test data remotely for analytics.
4.	ADAS (Advanced Driver Assistance Systems) Integration – Assesses drivers using automated safety features.
By Application
1.	Government Licensing Authorities – Automating driver license tests.
2.	Driving Schools and Training Centers – Improving driver training quality.
3.	Autonomous Vehicle Testing – Validating self-driving technology.
By End-User
1.	Public Sector (Transport Departments)
2.	Private Driving Schools
3.	Automotive OEMs (Autonomous Vehicle Developers)
